#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 17. Pāpabhikkhusutta → bhikkhusuttaṃ (bj) | bhikkhu (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Pāpabhikkhusutta"
msgstr "17. A Bad Monk"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.261"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn19.17:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ bhikkhuṃ vehāsaṃ "
"gacchantaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw "
"a monk flying through the air."

#. VAR: sajotibhūtā → sañjotibhūtā (s1-3, km) | sajotibhūto (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.17:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa saṅghāṭipi ādittā sampajjalitā sajotibhūtā, pattopi āditto "
"sampajjalito sajotibhūto, kāyabandhanampi ādittaṃ sampajjalitaṃ "
"sajotibhūtaṃ, kāyopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto."
msgstr "His outer robe, bowl, belt, and body were burning, blazing, and glowing"

msgctxt "sn19.17:1.3"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe …"
msgstr "as he screamed in pain. …” …"

msgctxt "sn19.17:1.4"
msgid ""
"eso, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kassapassa sammāsambuddhassa pāvacane pāpabhikkhu "
"ahosi … pe …."
msgstr ""
"“That monk used to be a bad monk in the time of Buddha Kassapa’s "
"dispensation. …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.17:1.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
